description: HOA APPROVED PET AMENDMENT! Enjoy sophisticated city living in this stunning corner 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom, luxury loft in Boston’s coveted Fort Point/Seaport district. In an exclusive stand-alone boutique building completely renovated in 2019 of only 11 units, this residence is delivered wholly finished in like-new condition with 10-foot ceilings and oversized windows, bathing the space in natural light and accentuating the hardwood floors. A thoughtfully designed layout maximizes living areas & functionality of private spaces. Huge closets provide exceptional storage, and bedrooms/bathrooms on are on opposite sides. At the heart of the home, the chef’s kitchen is a statement of luxury, featuring custom cabinetry, a Wolf gas range, an integrated Sub-Zero refrigerator, Bosch dishwasher, built-in microwave, and an expansive waterfall stone island—idyllic for both culinary enthusiasts and entertainers alike. Working gas fireplace in the living room. Seller offers $5,000 parking credit!
